It is putting out the lamp because the dawn has come.” - Rabindrana­th Tagore Deeply missed by loved ones Wife: Pauline Cheong Yeem Yoong Children: Sonia Tan Cui-Qing Leon Tan Yi-Ru Neil Tan Yi-Sheng Daren Tan Yi-Yao Siblings: Nancy Tan Henry Tan Ban Chuan Colin Tan Ban Lee Tan Ban Kwee Doris Tan
Tan Ban Teck And all friends and relatives Wake will be held from Tue 15.12.2020 to Wed 16.12.2020, from 12 noon to 11 pm (1 hour time slots).
Due to COVID restrictio­ns, please SMS / Whatsapp 9743 8032 for details on attending. There will be a private funeral for the family on Thu 17.12.2020. In lieu of wreaths, we ask that donations be made instead to the Bone Marrow Donor Program. ROBERT TAN BAN SENG Departed on 14 December 2020 With Deepest Sympathy & Heartfelt Condolence­s to The Family of The Late From: Management & Staff of ROBERT TAN PARTNERS PAC To our dearest JC classmate Pauline and family. With deepest condolence­s on the demise of your beloved husband and our dearest friend Robert. ROBERT TAN BAN SENG Departed on 14 December 2020 From: Management & Staff of QUESTOR MANAGEMENT PTE LTD With Deepest Sympathy & Heartfelt Condolence­s to The Family of The Late ROBERT TAN BAN SENG We truly miss the presence of a wonderful, gentle and kind man. May he Rest in Peace. Our prayers, hearts and minds are with you at this time. You will always have our love and support. From Robert Tan Ban Seng a.k.a. Deep Hole Agnes and Bien Bernie and Eugene Cecilia and Justin Christine and Yoon Leng Derek
Ead and Eugene Florence and Neville Helen and Richard Ines and Anand Jenny and Prabir Judy and Soon
Kee Ang and Eddie Lay Hong and Freddy Lay Lam and Allen Peena and Nigel Renee and Wei Savithri and Jeya Suzana Departed on 14 December 2020 Off on a new hashing adventure with the Heaven Hash
– with a cigar and a cold one in hand! On On Home, Deep Hole! You’ll be sorely missed! From: The Committee and Members of The Seletar Hash House Harriers For enquiries, call Obituaries 1800-289-9988 (weekdays 8.30am to 6.00pm) 6319-5192 PRINTED AND DISTRIBUTE­D BY PRESSREADE­R . PressReade­r.com +1 604 278 4604 ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY COPYRIGHT AND PROTECTED BY APPLICABLE LAW
